text: Michelle Bonae Finn-Burrell (born May 8, 1965) is an American former sprint athlete. She was born in Orlando, Florida. She won a gold medal at the 1992 Summer Olympics. She married Olympic gold medalist Leroy Burrell in 1992. They have three sons Cameron, Joshua and Jaden. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:American sprinters Category:Sportspeople from Orlando, Florida
